        <!-- HW4 -->
        <div id="theory" class="view-section">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <div class="mb-8"><button onclick="showDashboard()" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-white flex items-center gap-2 transition"><i data-lucide="arrow-left" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Back to Menu</button></div>
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-8">理論推導 Theory <span class="text-lg font-mono text-slate-500 ml-4">HW4</span></h2>
                <div class="glass-panel">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">折射震測公式證明</h3>
                    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                        <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 text-center">
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Travel Time Equation</p>
                            <span class="text-2xl text-white font-mono">$$ T = \frac{x}{V_2} + \frac{2h \cos \theta_c}{V_1} $$</span>
                        </div>
                         <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 text-center">
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Crossover Distance</p>
                            <span class="text-2xl text-white font-mono">$$ X_{cr} = 2h \sqrt{\frac{V_2 + V_1}{V_2 - V_1}} $$</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-8 text-slate-300 leading-loose">
                        <p>推導過程基於斯乃爾定律 (Snell's Law) 與幾何路徑分析。當震測剖面長度大於 $X_{cr}$ 時，折射波將比直達波更早到達接收器，此特性可用於判斷基盤深度。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

